{
  "chapter": 32,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十三回「血洗红旗」承接前章，谢晓峰在庙宇中听铁义讲述铁开诚的剑法来历——燕十三所传十三招毒辣剑法。雨后黄昏，谢晓峰来到红旗镖局客栈，与铁开诚对峙。铁开诚以镖旗被毁为由，要求谢晓峰留下珠花和鲜血洗旗。谢晓峰识破铁义编造的故事漏洞，揭露铁义企图借刀杀人的阴谋。铁义恼羞成怒偷袭，被谢晓峰一剑刺死。铁开诚与谢晓峰展开对决，铁开诚使出铁骑快剑\"乱弦式\"，谢晓峰却未拔剑，仅以剑上缎带应战，展现出超越常人的武学境界。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的武功，难道不是铁老镖头传授的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁义",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大部分都是，只不过他的剑法，又比老镖头多出了十三招。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知道这十三招剑法是什么人传授给他的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁义",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁义",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "燕十三。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有人毁了我们一面镖旗，就等于将我们千千万万面镖旗全都毁了，此仇不报，此辱不洗，江湖中就再也看不见我们的镖旗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你又来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你应该知道我一定会来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为你一定听了很多话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是非曲直，你当然一定已分得很清楚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你掌中无剑？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "剑在你心里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "心中是不是有剑，至少你总该看得出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "心中若有剑，杀气在眉睫。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的掌中无剑，心中亦无剑，你的剑在哪里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在你手里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的剑就是你的剑？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不懂？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁义",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不懂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你就未免太糊涂了些。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁义",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我本来就是个糊涂人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "糊涂人为什么偏偏要说谎？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁义",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁……谁说了谎？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你编了个很好的故事，也演了很动人的一出戏，戏里的每个角色都配合得很好，情节也很紧凑，只可惜其中还有一两点漏洞。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁义",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "漏洞？什么漏洞？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁老镖头发丧三天之后，铁开诚就将那四个人逐出了镖局？再命你去暗中追杀？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁义",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是你不忍下手，只拿了四件血衣回去交差？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁义",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁开诚就相信了你？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_yi",
      "speaker_name": "铁义",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他一向相信我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是被你杀了的那四个人，今天却忽然复活了，铁开诚亲眼看见了他们，居然还同样相信你，还叫你去追查他们的来历，难道他是个呆子？可是他看来为什么又偏偏不像？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若想要我替你除去铁开诚，若想要我们鹬蚌相争，让你渔翁得利，你就该编个更好一点的故事，至少也该弄清楚，那么样一朵珠花，绝不是三百两银子能买得到的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你早就知道我一定会再来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我听了很多话，你相信我一定可以听出其中的破绽。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为你是谢晓峰。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是不是准备请我喝两杯？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我一向滴酒不沾。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "独饮无趣，看来我只好走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在你还不能走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还得留下两样东西。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要我留下什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "留下那朵珠花。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "珠花？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那是我用三百两银子买来送给别人的，不能送给你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真是你买的？真是你叫铁义去买的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "丝毫不假。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是那么样一朵珠花，价值最少已在八百两以上，三百两怎能买得到？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天宝号的掌柜，本是红旗镖局的账房，所以价钱算得特别便宜，何况珠宝一业，利润最厚，他以这价钱卖给我，也没有亏本！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "除了珠花外，你还得留下你的血，来洗我的镖旗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是个聪明人，实在很聪明。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "聪明人一文钱可以买一堆。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我本不想杀你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我却非杀你不可。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有件事我也非问清楚不可。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁中奇老镖头，是不是你的亲生父亲？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他究竟是怎么死的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两柄虽然是在同一炉中炼出来的，却有轻重之分。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你惯用的是哪一柄！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一炉炼出的剑有七柄，七柄剑我都用得很趁手，这一点我已占了便宜。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无妨。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的剑法虽然以快得胜，可是高手相争，还是以重为强。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我明白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我既不愿将较重的一柄剑给你，也不愿再占你这个便宜，只有大家各凭自己的运气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请，请先选一柄。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    }
